profile: Over 14 years of experience serving Peterborough, the Kawarthas and the surrounding areas. YS General Contracting specializes in both interior & exterior renovations, custom decks, fences and additions. Locally owned and operated since 2005, we ensure any renovation project is completed in a timely manner and always remains within your desired budget. Each project is given special attention to detail from start to finish and our team of highly skilled contractors strive to bring your vision to reality.
